## Key Features

- 🧭 **Full-featured navigation**: Sidebar navigation, breadcrumbs, and more
- 🔍 **Search**: Built-in site search
- 📱 **Responsive**: Optimized for mobile devices
- 🌙 **Dark mode**: Light and dark theme support
- 🎨 **Customizable**: Flexible styling options
- 📝 **Markdown & MDX**: Write content using Markdown and MDX

