## Getting Started with Starlight

To create your own Starlight documentation site, follow these steps:

```bash
# Create a new project
npm create astro@latest -- --template starlight

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start the development server
npm run dev
```

Visit the [Starlight documentation](https://starlight.astro.build/) for more information.
